{"tid":192863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息指美軍航母戰鬥群駛往朝鮮半島附近","createTime":"2017-04-09T01:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T04:33:44.000Z","uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f30d408764a592a7525e3d2246cb93be14fdd871","tid":192863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"消息指美軍航母戰鬥群駛往朝鮮半島附近<br />\n有報道引述美國官員說，美軍卡爾文森號航空母艦戰鬥群，將會駛往朝鮮半島附近的西太平洋。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=933700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D933700&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=44344dfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=933700</a>"},{"pid":"44f8e276fd273174e53bcfd8ae11d90271b6c4a6","tid":192863,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9b520bad21b7e798a5e904cb2d956075aa964c","tid":192863,"uid":7421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"金仔起左身未呀"},{"pid":"e64299650ba148b1dbfc871e9cde61ff145cfa0a","tid":192863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66fa97d4713fdcd51337935df730d78548db0e1","tid":192863,"uid":65320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"侵侵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然似做樣<br />\n點都好過黑鬼 樣都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b9b7375828e3f8a630b8b4be808899f53bdccd","tid":192863,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca94e3043e13df4d5d7570fa966fedbb320b3862","tid":192863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔起左身未呀</blockquote><br />\n好驚驚！？"},{"pid":"b3d272312035360b2859443fe9665002d4e21f7b","tid":192863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"因應北韓局勢 美官員：航母打擊群將赴朝鮮半島<br />\n<br />\n2017-04-09 08:37<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日前川習會舉行前一天，北韓向朝鮮半島東部海域發射飛毛腿飛彈，讓東北亞局勢高度緊張。有外媒報導指出，一位美國官員透露，為了因應北韓的嚴峻局勢，美軍航母卡爾文森號（Carl Vinson）打擊群即將前往鄰近朝鮮半島的西太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一位不願具名的美國官員指出，鑑於北韓在飛彈武器發展所造成的擔憂，美國海軍卡爾文森號航母打擊群將從新加坡駛往朝鮮半島，以便因應北韓令人憂心的行為。該名官員還說，我們認為增加存在的動作是有必要的。<br />\n<br />\n近年來北韓試射飛彈的頻率漸增，北韓領導人金正恩也多次預告，今年還會有類似舉動的可能，尤其是本月15日北韓總統金日成冥誕105週年，屆時北韓一舉一動將受到各界關注。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpgboByr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpgboByr.jpg&h=e3ebf2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2030414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2030414&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1ed54e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2030414&h=96677504\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2030414</a>"},{"pid":"39e897fa0e32981f4054af6b989f12be379e00c7","tid":192863,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金仔起左身未呀</blockquote><br />\n好驚驚！？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n失禁尿牀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5376ee3671eba11695aa6ed7d801826dbc31b9a0","tid":192863,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"WW3 <img src=\"/assets/