3:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔: 即刻叫歡樂組準備</blockquote><br />\n幫佢打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81be12854ec912d05c9871d4398a08f94820495e","tid":192863,"uid":104148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ad86814dd19ad787d4c37aaeb26310e1aa50d9c8","tid":192863,"uid":83000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170404/mobile/bknint-20170404171246688-0404_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170404%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170404171246688-0404_17011_001.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=10fe7e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170404/mobile/bknint-20170404171246688-0404_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩支以兩棲攻擊艦為首的遠征戰鬥群，目前分別位於東海及南海。它們搭載大批海軍陸戰隊兵力，屬於朝鮮半島爆發戰爭時，最先投入作戰的登陸部隊。"}]}